span.font:
The main data structure here is a
double-ended queue, backed by an AVL tree.
They store data at their root and leaves.
In our use case, the roots store an optional
auction_outcome, and the leaves store
liquidation_slice's.
Branches are not a part of the public
interface, therefore not shown in this diagram.
